		<title>Mayo Clinic researchers identify key DNA changes in the brains of people with Alzheimer&amp;#8217;s disease</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-identify-key-dna-changes-in-the-brains-of-people-with-alzheimers-disease/</link>
		
