		<title>Tomorrow&amp;#8217;s Cure: Shortening the diagnostic journey</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/tomorrows-cure-shortening-the-diagnostic-journey/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[jftmayo]]></dc:creator>
